originalText.text:
PLEASE READ!!!!!
There are no Coach Outlets in NYC. There is a Coach Retail store inside Macy’s at Herald Square and another one in The Shops at Hudson Yards but NO OUTLET. The closest Outlet stores are at Jersey Gardens, NJ and Woodbury Commons, NY. If you are looking for any aftersale services in the area go to Hudson Yards for assistance.

originalText.text: Coach men’s shoes are top quality and last for years while always looking great.  There is a guy on Tik Tok that takes apart leather goods from all the top fashion houses and he always says Coach uses top grade leather, stitching, and hardware.  He also says Coach is the most fairly priced.  Its easy to order items on the Coach website and pay with Amazon.  My two cents for Coach leadership -  they just need to tighten up their branding and design offerings in order to compete with LV, Prada, etc.
